{"tid":1457876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當日佢都無怪過其他人","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:55:50.000Z","uid":25382,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0cb602fc18038fc76bb19c336b02b7c9d70cf6","tid":1457876,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K0EmC0VOdzI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK0EmC0VOdzI&d=5%2F0N1eX%2FnGDFGLWAFE16zurBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=64ea5c86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K0EmC0VOdzI</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰</span><br />\n大家仲記唔記得成場運動嘅核心價值<br />\n71死士當日明知留低係十死無生<br />\n佢都無怪責其他人<br />\n反而講出「兄弟爬山，各自努力」尊重其他人嘅決定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">去</span>或者<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">留</span>從來都只係好似買大細咁<br />\n買啱咗嘅無需要去怪責其他人<br />\n買錯咗嘅亦請你尊重相反意見嘅人<br />\n檢討可以，但係指責就萬萬不可"},{"pid":"54205772547c542e76318dcdf24a8d30ab7531eb","tid":1457876,"uid":254361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n用下個腦諗嘢<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n你哋唔好喺度發文喺度煽動<br />\n佢地成功分化我地了啦<br />\n<br />\n和理非非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里而的大反派說了這麼幾句 <br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後這再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"e7de58dc9c2d785313882c72cb2c3215e35140fd","tid":1457876,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b6460e99b76010475a7b9fdeb6be327723f93145","tid":1457876,"uid":25382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:35:24.000Z","msg":"今日揀錯咗<br />\n咪聽日再揀過囉<br />\n今日係咩都無輸過架"},{"pid":"f607c14687cac26edbebfa693be8af4c85883a6a","tid":1457876,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f951785435361400e4802a6a6fa6d7294b28aa6f","tid":1457876,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fd80d7c96d49abefbe90583eae49a74be88f1322","tid":1457876,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89e2665d1fe80cbf4f3948e4d19cefda1d0b60ad","tid":1457876,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:49:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不分化"},{"pid":"f088933703500ec734fd8063a0eb8410a01037da","tid":1457876,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"聽日1點機場見<br />\n不撤不散"}]}